.SH VERSION
.PP
v3.4.2 and above
.SH EXAMPLES
.IP \[bu] 2
Decrease the current value.
.RS 2
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
>\ sequence.getCurrentValue()
1000
>\ sequence.setCurrentValue(\ 500\ )
\f[]
.fi
.PP
Error message:
.IP
.nf
