(shell):1\ uncaught\ exception:\ \-358
Sequence\ value\ has\ been\ used
\f[]
.fi
.RE
.IP \[bu] 2
Increase the current value.
.RS 2
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
>\ sequence.getCurrentValue()
1000
>\ sequence.setCurrentValue(\ 2000\ )
\f[]
.fi
.PP
Current value after setting:
.IP
